                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310908-204-off1053 t18310908-204-crimeloc1056"></join>. On the 30th of July, I was informed that a person had taken a handkerchief, which had hung by the door; I looked and missed it; I had seen it about an hour before - I went to the door, and the officer brought the prisoner back with it.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18310908-204-person1539">
                  JOHN 
                  MADDY
               <interp inst="t18310908-204-person1539" type="surname" value="MADDY"></interp>
