                     <interp inst="t18310908-204-person1539" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am an officer. I met the prisoner coming towards Rosemary-lane, about two hundred yards from the prosecutor's; a young man from the shop overtook him, and said he had stolen a handkerchief: he denied it, but I saw him drop this handkerchief from his jacket - I took it up, and took charge of him.</p>
               <p>The prisoner pleaded poverty.</p>
